{
  "stem": "27759.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I scored the highest out of all the men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was Morse code.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they put me in the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] air base security battalion--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to transmit-- that was at Camp Rucker, Alabama.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I said goodbye to my mother and dad, and my-- there was two other brothers and myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to downtown to the B and O station to ship out for various designations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my fiancee, she was there, along with her sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a twin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] saw me off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told her-- I said, I will get married, but it wouldn't be fair to my mother, and because a-- on induction, they got-- each soldier was insured for $10,000.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, if anything happened to me, we would have not been married long enough for your entitlement to this $10,000.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, my mother has done more for me up to this point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I named my mother as the beneficiary if anything should happen to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, as I promised her, after the war, we got married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from the marriage, we had three sons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I arrived at Fort Meade, Maryland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got the necessary inoculation shots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then from Fort Meade, I was shipped to Camp Rucker, Alabama.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my other brothers, one was sent to-- Fort Belvoir, Virginia, do and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my baby brother was sent to [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a camp in Michigan.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember just what the name of the camp was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at first, the outfit that I was in, the lowest rank was corporal technician.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
